name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 67: A tampon box full of corn dogs

content.html:
Dear Internet, Well, Nick is out of town again, but that means we can have another special guest on! This we we have Carly Shields on! Unfortunately Nick will be gone next week too. Yeah…we maybe shouldn’t only record on weekends now that we are vaccinated. Anyway… On this week’s show we talk about hoggin all the snacks, secret snack drawers, piercing your own ear, and the importance of incognito. We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
